Interface NamedQueryMemento

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    NamedCallableQueryMemento, NamedHqlQueryMemento, NamedNativeQueryMemento, NamedQueryProducer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractNamedQueryMemento

    public interface NamedQueryMemento
    Named Query mementos are stored in the QueryEngine's NamedQueryRepository. This is the base contract for all specific types of named query mementos
